                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This young man's woman offered me 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and I took 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. of it; but I found I was doing wrong, and I would take no more of the 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. which I had agreed to take—his young woman took me home that morning.</p>
